{"tid":1807974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"主權在民 香港獨立","createTime":"2020-01-02T05:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-02T06:08:05.000Z","uid":309148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e41c2f9e552b6bd6bb8dc458a0f8cb4feb30c640","tid":1807974,"uid":309148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T05:43:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主權在民 香港獨立</span><br />\n係咪覺得香港獨立唯一出路嗰獨立唔夠focus？<br />\n依家有啦<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">主權在民 香港獨立</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主權在民 香港獨立</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主權在民 香港獨立</span><br />\n<br />\n香港的主權 只屬於香港人 香港民族<br />\n尋求獨立 是天理 具正當性和合法性<br />\n北方極權同港共政府剽取左香港人嘅權力<br />\n一步一步嘅迫害 從來冇真正咁尊重過香港人<br />\n孰可忍孰不可忍<br />\n今天尋求獨立之意 也是迫不得已<br />\n為求香港民族安生立命<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主權在民 香港獨立</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主權在民 香港獨立</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">主權在民 香港獨立</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：本人唔係獨派 但係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">絕對唔會割！！！</span>"},{"pid":"da8ae0389c20496f33acf7eaa819f231eb4a1f15","tid":1807974,"uid":309148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-02T06:08:05.000Z","msg":"tui"}]}